  "title": "Architectural Drafter",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate with site personnel to prepare drawings to meet project needs</li>\n  <li>Prepare and check drawings as per project requirements</li>\n  <li>Prepare and archive submission of shop drawings and as-built drawings</li>\n  <li>Ad-hoc duties as assigned by Architectural Manager</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's Degree in Engineering (Civil), Architecture or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Required skill(s): AutoCad, Revit, SketchUp</li>\n  <li><strong>Experience in MRT (Architectural) </strong>works will be a bonus</li>\n  <li>At least 2 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>\n</ul>",
